ŪTO THE MEMORY OF
WAYFARER (W. M. ROBINSON)
WHO DIED 17TH SEPTEMBER 1956
HIS DEVOTION TO THE PASTIME OF CYCLING
INSPIRED MANY TO ENJOY THE COUNTRYSIDE
AND THE OPEN ROAD
